{
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "description": "Per-deployment view: utilization vs requests/limits, pod state, restart trend, and Loki logs scoped to the selected deployment. Pick namespace + workload from the variables above.",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "fixedColor": "blue",
            "mode": "fixed"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(kube_deployment_spec_replicas{namespace=\"$namespace\", deployment=\"$workload\"}) or vector(0)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Desired Replicas",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "/^ready$/",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(kube_deployment_status_replicas_ready{namespace=\"$namespace\", deployment=\"$workload\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "ready",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(kube_deployment_spec_replicas{namespace=\"$namespace\", deployment=\"$workload\"}) or vector(0)",
          "hide": true,
          "legendFormat": "desired",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Ready",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(kube_deployment_status_replicas_unavailable{namespace=\"$namespace\", deployment=\"$workload\"}) or vector(0)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Unavailable",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "decimals": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 5
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(\n  increase(kube_pod_container_status_restarts_total{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[1h])\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n) or vector(0)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Pod Restarts (last 1h)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "none"
            }
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "requests"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "blue",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.lineStyle",
                "value": {
                  "dash": [
                    10,
                    10
                  ],
                  "fill": "dash"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.fillOpacity",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "limits"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "red",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.lineStyle",
                "value": {
                  "dash": [
                    10,
                    10
                  ],
                  "fill": "dash"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.fillOpacity",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "usage"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "green",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "mean",
            "max",
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(\n  node_namespace_pod_container:container_cpu_usage_seconds_total:sum_irate{namespace=\"$namespace\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "legendFormat": "usage",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(\n  kube_pod_container_resource_requests{namespace=\"$namespace\", resource=\"cpu\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "legendFormat": "requests",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(\n  kube_pod_container_resource_limits{namespace=\"$namespace\", resource=\"cpu\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "legendFormat": "limits",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "CPU — Usage vs Requests vs Limits",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "none"
            }
          },
          "unit": "bytes"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "requests"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "blue",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.lineStyle",
                "value": {
                  "dash": [
                    10,
                    10
                  ],
                  "fill": "dash"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.fillOpacity",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "limits"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "red",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.lineStyle",
                "value": {
                  "dash": [
                    10,
                    10
                  ],
                  "fill": "dash"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.fillOpacity",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "usage"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "fixedColor": "green",
                  "mode": "fixed"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 13
      },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "mean",
            "max",
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(\n  container_memory_working_set_bytes{namespace=\"$namespace\", container!=\"\", image!=\"\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "legendFormat": "usage",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(\n  kube_pod_container_resource_requests{namespace=\"$namespace\", resource=\"memory\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "legendFormat": "requests",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(\n  kube_pod_container_resource_limits{namespace=\"$namespace\", resource=\"memory\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "legendFormat": "limits",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Memory — Usage vs Requests vs Limits",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto"
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Phase"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "options": {
                      "Failed": {
                        "color": "red",
                        "index": 2
                      },
                      "Pending": {
                        "color": "yellow",
                        "index": 1
                      },
                      "Running": {
                        "color": "green",
                        "index": 0
                      },
                      "Succeeded": {
                        "color": "blue",
                        "index": 3
                      },
                      "Unknown": {
                        "color": "orange",
                        "index": 4
                      }
                    },
                    "type": "value"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Ready"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "options": {
                      "0": {
                        "color": "red",
                        "index": 1,
                        "text": "No"
                      },
                      "1": {
                        "color": "green",
                        "index": 0,
                        "text": "Yes"
                      }
                    },
                    "type": "value"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Restarts"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "color": "green",
                      "value": null
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "yellow",
                      "value": 1
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "red",
                      "value": 5
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Last Reason"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "options": {
                      "Completed": {
                        "color": "blue",
                        "index": 5
                      },
                      "ContainerCannotRun": {
                        "color": "red",
                        "index": 2
                      },
                      "DeadlineExceeded": {
                        "color": "orange",
                        "index": 3
                      },
                      "Error": {
                        "color": "orange",
                        "index": 1
                      },
                      "Evicted": {
                        "color": "orange",
                        "index": 4
                      },
                      "OOMKilled": {
                        "color": "red",
                        "index": 0
                      }
                    },
                    "type": "value"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Last Exit"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "options": {
                      "0": {
                        "color": "green",
                        "index": 0,
                        "text": "0 (clean)"
                      },
                      "137": {
                        "color": "red",
                        "index": 1,
                        "text": "137 (OOMKill)"
                      },
                      "139": {
                        "color": "red",
                        "index": 2,
                        "text": "139 (SIGSEGV)"
                      },
                      "143": {
                        "color": "blue",
                        "index": 3,
                        "text": "143 (SIGTERM)"
                      }
                    },
                    "type": "value"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "color": "green",
                      "value": null
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "orange",
                      "value": 1
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 26
      },
      "id": 7,
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "max by (pod, phase) (\n  kube_pod_status_phase{namespace=\"$namespace\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n) > 0",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "phase",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum by (pod) (\n  kube_pod_container_status_restarts_total{namespace=\"$namespace\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "restarts",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum by (pod) (\n  kube_pod_status_ready{namespace=\"$namespace\", condition=\"true\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "ready",
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "expr": "max by (pod, reason) (\n  kube_pod_container_status_last_terminated_reason{namespace=\"$namespace\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n) > 0",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "reason",
          "refId": "D"
        },
        {
          "expr": "max by (pod) (\n  kube_pod_container_status_last_terminated_exitcode{namespace=\"$namespace\"}\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "exitcode",
          "refId": "E"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Pods",
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "joinByField",
          "options": {
            "byField": "pod",
            "mode": "outer"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time 1": true,
              "Time 2": true,
              "Time 3": true,
              "Time 4": true,
              "Time 5": true,
              "Value #A": true,
              "Value #D": true
            },
            "indexByName": {
              "Value #B": 3,
              "Value #C": 2,
              "Value #E": 5,
              "phase": 1,
              "pod": 0,
              "reason": 4
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "Value #B": "Restarts",
              "Value #C": "Ready",
              "Value #E": "Last Exit",
              "phase": "Phase",
              "pod": "Pod",
              "reason": "Last Reason"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear"
          },
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 33
      },
      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (pod) (\n  rate(kube_pod_container_status_restarts_total{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[5m])\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "legendFormat": "{{pod}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Container Restarts — Rate (5m)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "${loki_datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 14,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 39
      },
      "id": 9,
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": false,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "showLabels": false,
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{namespace=\"$namespace\", pod=~\"$workload-.*\"}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Logs",
      "type": "logs"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "description": "Each spike = one OOMKill restart event for this workload. Derived from kube-state-metrics (restart counter + last termination reason filter), not from cAdvisor's container_oom_events_total — that metric exists but doesn't increment reliably on cgroup v2 + k3s because the cgroup is destroyed faster than cAdvisor can poll it. KSM gets the truth via the kubelet pod-status API. Caveat: only catches OOMs where OOMKilled is still the *most recent* restart reason; a later non-OOM restart would mask earlier OOMs.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "fixedColor": "red",
            "mode": "fixed"
          },
          "custom": {
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "none"
            }
          },
          "decimals": 0,
          "max": null,
          "min": 0,
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 22
      },
      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (pod) (\n  (\n    increase(kube_pod_container_status_restarts_total{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])\n    * on(pod, namespace, container) group_left()\n    (kube_pod_container_status_last_terminated_reason{namespace=\"$namespace\", reason=\"OOMKilled\"} == 1)\n  )\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(workload)\n  namespace_workload_pod:kube_pod_owner:relabel{namespace=\"$namespace\", workload=\"$workload\", workload_type=\"deployment\"}\n)",
          "legendFormat": "{{pod}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "OOM Events",
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
